6pfi2SCSFxDA7sXRwMnVmXc5C1239jOhUIZAsZ.jpg',NULL,'United Kingdom','England','London',51.5074000,-0.1278000,1,0,0,5,'London - England\'s Capital | Travel Destination',NULL,'<p>Discover London, UK. Book tours, hotels, and experiences in England\'s historic capital.</p>','2025-05-25 02:01:53','2025-09-16 12:30:25',NULL,'01 Tour, 02 Hotel'),(6,'Barcelona','barcelona','<p>The cosmopolitan capital of Spain\'s Catalonia region, known for Sagrada Familia and Park G&uuml;ell</p>','uploads/custom-images/KnFv2T5Vk2FoMCiunHWPA5tbtHK7vPG0b4sjlAmQ.jpg',NULL,'Spain','Catalonia','Barcelona',41.3851000,2.1734000,1,0,0,6,'Barcelona - Catalonia\'s Gem | Travel Destination',NULL,'<p>Visit Barcelona, Spain. Book tours, hotels, and experiences in this vibrant Catalan city.</p>','2025-05-25 02:01:53','2025-09-16 12:30:24',NULL,'01 Tour, 02 Hotel'),(7,'Dubai','dubai','<p>A city of superlatives, with the world\'s tallest building and luxury shopping</p>','uploads/custom-images/kQfcYdSCWMVmkLXSpIPgvdPxjOR6hPAIlOZiPvZ1.jpg',NULL,'United Arab Emirates','Dubai','Dubai',25.2048000,55.2708000,1,0,0,7,'Dubai - City of Gold | Travel Destination',NULL,'<p>Experience Dubai, UAE. Book tours, hotels, and experiences in this ultramodern desert city.</p>','2025-05-25 02:01:53','2025-09-16 12:30:23',NULL,'01 Tour, 02 Hotel'),(11,'ANTALYA','Antalya_Turkey','<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>&nbsp;Discover the Magic of Antalya: Where the Mountains Meet the Mediterranean</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">From the pine-covered hills of <strong>Kemer</strong>, nestled between rugged mountains and turquoise sea, to the golden beaches and ancient ruins of <strong>Side</strong> and <strong>Alanya</strong>, the <strong>Antalya region</strong> is a wonderland of contrasts and unforgettable experiences.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Wander through the lively streets of <strong>Antalya city,</strong> take in the breathtaking views from<strong> Alanya Castle</strong>, relax in <strong>luxury resorts in Bele</strong>k, or stroll along the <strong>palm-lined coast of Lara</strong> &ndash; just minutes from the airport.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Whether you crave <strong>adrenaline </strong>(rafting, paragliding, jeep safaris), <strong>culture</strong> (ancient theaters, Ottoman bazaars), or <strong>wellness </strong>(authentic Turkish hammam, spa retreats), Antalya delivers it all &ndash; and more.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Don&rsquo;t just visit. Live it.</strong><br>Sunsets on a pirate-style boat cruise. Ancient cities rising from the sand. Forest hikes ending in waterfalls. Flavors that awaken your senses. Moments you&rsquo;ll brag about.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>This is not just a holiday. This is your Antalya story and adventure!&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','uploads/custom-images/2vpkGlhgq0pXS0Duds2CPLLo7L1Ne5ZrEq96jiwj.jpg','destinations/zkFC3coD3DoxfdsZJy8bUuoWUjkNhFvfSKR0UCcS.jpg','TURKEY',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-08-19 13:05:04','2025-09-16 12:30:43',20,'ANTALYA, ALANYA, BELEK, LARA, KEMER, SIDE - TURKEY, TURKYE, TURCIA, Turkiye'),(12,'Crete','crete','<p>Crete is the largest and most populous of the Greek islands, the 88th largest island in the world, and the fifth largest island in the Mediterranean Sea, after Sicily, Sardinia, Cyprus, and Corsica. Crete is located approximately 100 km south of the Peloponnese, and about 300 km southwest of Anatolia.</p>','uploads/custom-images/xcFvsfoT8C8QpLu34kVg1t55fTdQiQrbWWwBGO19.jpg','destinations/9dzofhG4g9I4BknMKUeCAEG2dUjonWBXTPRqPI6w.jpg','GREECE',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,0,0,'Crete, imply Has It All!',NULL,'<p>Simply Has It All! Crete is&nbsp;<strong>the largest island in Greece, and the fifth largest one in the Mediterranean Sea</strong>. Here, you can admire the remnants of brilliant civilizations, explore glorious beaches, impressive mountainscapes, fertile valleys and steep gorges, and become part of the island\'s rich gastronomic culture.</p>','2025-09-03 10:47:28','2025-11-20 10:29:40',2,'greece, seaviews'),(13,'Durres','durres','<p><strong>Durr&euml;s, Albania: Where Ancient History Meets Adriatic Charm.</strong> Discover Durr&euml;s, Albania\'s vibrant coastal city, a captivating blend of millennia-old history and sun-drenched Adriatic beauty. Explore the magnificent Roman Amphitheatre, wander through ancient ruins, and then unwind on golden beaches. With its lively promenade, delicious seafood, and easy access to Tirana, Durr&euml;s offers an authentic Albanian experience that\'s both enriching and relaxing.</p>','uploads/custom-images/aOy04ho26WsdAjfR9hfmFOteyLHzMzn6xjKvzKM9.jpg','destinations/MMmKA1XPJlmZyHvDWVexQsCjpIE51yTUDuKqxb91.jpg','Albania',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,0,'Durrës, Albania: Ancient Wonders, Golden Beaches. Your Adriatic adventure starts here! 🏛️🏖️ #Durres #Albania #Travel',NULL,'<p><strong>Your Adriatic Escape Awaits in Durr&euml;s, Albania.</strong> Imagine a destination where the echoes of Roman emperors mingle with the gentle lapping of the Adriatic Sea. Welcome to Durr&euml;s, Albania. Spend your mornings exploring the awe-inspiring Roman Amphitheatre and the Byzantine Forum, then dedicate your afternoons to the city\'s beautiful, family-friendly beaches. Stroll along the vibrant Lungomare, savor exquisite seafood at a waterfront restaurant, and immerse yourself in the lively atmosphere of this historic port city. With its rich past, inviting coastline, and easy accessibility, Durr&euml;s offers a perfect blend of cultural discovery and seaside relaxation for an unforgettable Albanian adventure.</p>','2025-09-03 15:03:46','2025-12-19 14:12:58',2,'beach'),(14,'ISTANBUL','istanbul','<h3>Discover Istanbul: Where East Meets West in an Unforgettable City Break, Tour or Excursion</h3>\r\n<p>Embark on a captivating journey to Istanbul, a city where ancient history and modern vibrancy coexist on two continents. As the ultimate destination for city breaks, tours, and experiences, Istanbul offers a rich tapestry of culture, adventure, and flavor for every type of traveler.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For the History and Culture Buffs:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Step back in time as you explore the city&rsquo;s majestic past. Our <strong>\"Cultural &amp; Historic\"</strong> city breaks bring you to the heart of the Byzantine and Ottoman Empires. Wander through the Hagia Sophia, a masterpiece of architecture, and stand in awe of the intricate beauty of the Blue Mosque. Discover the opulence of the Topkapi Palace, where sultans once reigned, and lose yourself in the atmospheric passages of the Basilica Cistern. A guided tour of these UNESCO World Heritage sites is essential for understanding the soul of this incredible city.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For the Adventurous and Curious:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Ready for an adventure? Our <strong>\"Adventure &amp; Nature\"</strong> tours are designed to thrill. Take a ferry to the Princes\' Islands for a day of car-free exploration, cycling through serene pine forests and past elegant Ottoman mansions. Climb the Galata Tower for a breathtaking 360-degree panoramic view of the city and the Bosphorus, a perfect photo opportunity. For an authentic experience, get lost in the labyrinthine corridors of the Grand Bazaar, one of the world\'s oldest and largest covered markets, where you can haggle for unique souvenirs and spices.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For the Foodies and Romantics:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Istanbul is a feast for the senses, and our <strong>\"City Break Gastronomic\"</strong> experiences are a must. Savor the diverse flavors of Turkish cuisine with a street food tour, from a warm balik-ekmek (fish sandwich) under the Galata Bridge to a traditional Turkish breakfast. In the evening, a <strong>\"Romantic &amp; Spa\"</strong> package might include a relaxing hammam (Turkish bath) followed by a magical Bosphorus cruise by night, where the city\'s illuminated palaces and mosques cast a mesmerizing glow on the water.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For Families and Friends:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Istanbul is a vibrant playground for all ages. Our <strong>\"Family Friendly\"</strong> packages include fun-filled activities like a visit to Miniat&uuml;rk, a park with miniature replicas of Turkey\'s most famous landmarks, or a trip to the Istanbul Aquarium. A ride on the historic red tram along Istiklal Street offers a charming way to see the city\'s lively modern side.</p>\r\n<p>With our meticulously crafted itineraries and optional activities, you can customize your Istanbul experience to be as relaxed or as action-packed as you desire. From historical tours and sunset cruises to culinary workshops and lively nightlife, Istanbul awaits.</p>','uploads/custom-images/pJX6ptrvfGddUI2myjp5jm0ek4CStDbmSyVuPehP.jpg','destinations/Eq8orQTh8nNFZDmL9JSbhUarOWBcONVfYSJJdr2I.jpg','TURKEY',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,0,0,'Istanbul City Breaks: Tours & Unique Experiences at a Cultural Crossroads',NULL,'<p>Discover Istanbul: book cultural, adventure, and romantic city breaks. Our tours and experiences offer a unique journey into the heart of Turkey\'s vibrant metropolis.</p>','2025-09-12 10:32:28','2025-09-16 12:30:19',2,'Istanbul, Istanbul City Break, Istanbul Tours, Istanbul Travel, Istanbul experiences, Istanbul CIty Breaks, Istanbul Excursions, Discover Istanbul, Family Friendly Istanbul, Cultural Istanbul, Romantic Istanbul, Istanbul Adventure'),(15,'Munich','munich','<p>Get ready to fall for Munich, a city where legendary traditions and cutting-edge cool collide.</p>\r\n<p>Forget everything you think you know about city breaks. This is your chance to step into a place where a vibrant, cosmopolitan spirit dances with centuries-old Bavarian soul. Picture this: you\'re raising a stein in a beer garden that\'s been around for generations, then moments later, you\'re lost in a world-class art gallery or exploring a stunning royal palace that looks like it\'s from a fairytale.</p>\r\n<p>This isn\'t just a trip; it\'s an adventure waiting to happen. From the electric energy of the world-famous Oktoberfest to the serene beauty of the Isar River, every corner of Munich offers an experience that will stay with you long after you\'ve left.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Don\'t miss out on the chance to make memories you\'ll be telling stories about for years. Your Munich adventure starts now!</strong></p>','uploads/custom-images/KFIfdph2K8DiiLIjvAazNNpxNLiRhmaX1ALrPcnV.jpg','destinations/30w7sl9O8cVYLkiO1XaWIKvGjfVo1UEDIqSBl2Z0.jpg','Germany',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,0,0,'Munich Guide: Top Tours, Activities, City Breaks, & Travel Tips',NULL,'<p>Discover Munich! Explore historic landmarks, vibrant beer gardens, and unique Bavarian culture. Find the best city breaks, tours, and travel tips for your trip. Excursions and<strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-61af7619-7fff-a0ef-4a11-f85d5075d48a\"> things to do in Munich: Oktoberfest, Bavarian culture, Marienplatz, English Garden, Neuschwanstein Castle, Munich attractions. </strong></p>','2025-09-15 12:51:58','2025-11-20 10:28:36',2,'Munich, city break Munich, Munich tours, things to do in Munich, Munich travel guide, Oktoberfest, Bavarian culture, Marienplatz, English Garden, Neuschwanstein Castle, Munich attractions.'),(16,'BERLIN','berlin',NULL,'uploads/custom-images/rK12jilo3b8jtbCJVNndjlaxKsTA7LC6m61xyecR.jpg','destinations/TZ5phqLks8b3N3mVVxfTES67xkC3f670uxgL5nVt.jpg','Germany',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-17 08:52:26','2025-11-17 13:17:54',2,NULL),(17,'TUNISIA','tunisia','<p data-start=\"862\" data-end=\"891\">Tunisia vacation activities, Tunisia private tours, Tunisia guided tours, Family activities Tunisia, Tunisia UNESCO sites, Tunisia history tours, Tunisia adventure tours, North Africa travel experiences, Tunisia holiday activities, Tunisia nature &amp; wildlife tours Authentic Tunisia, hidden gems Tunisia, cultural authenticity, Mediterranean charm, North African heritage, Berber culture experiences</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1456\" data-end=\"1491\"><strong data-start=\"1460\" data-end=\"1491\">Hammamet / Yasmi