egypt','<p data-start=\"882\" data-end=\"1164\">Egypt is a destination that feels alive in every moment - a place where&nbsp;<strong data-start=\"989\" data-end=\"1016\">5000-year-old pyramids</strong>, ancient temples, and sacred tombs coexist with <strong data-start=\"1065\" data-end=\"1083\">turquoise bays</strong>, vibrant reefs, luxurious resorts and the warm hospitality of the Red Sea coast.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1166\" data-end=\"1412\">From the monumental <strong data-start=\"1186\" data-end=\"1206\">Pyramids of Giza</strong>, the <strong data-start=\"1212\" data-end=\"1222\">Sphinx</strong>, and the extraordinary treasures of the Egyptian Museum, to the majestic <strong data-start=\"1296\" data-end=\"1311\">Nile Valley</strong>, <strong data-start=\"1313\" data-end=\"1322\">Luxor</strong>, and <strong data-start=\"1328\" data-end=\"1338\">Karnak</strong>, Egypt is a curated journey through the world&rsquo;s most iconic civilization.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1414\" data-end=\"1757\">But Egypt is more than history. Along the Red Sea, places like <strong data-start=\"1477\" data-end=\"1489\">Hurghada</strong>, <strong data-start=\"1491\" data-end=\"1505\">Makadi Bay</strong>, <strong data-start=\"1507\" data-end=\"1519\">El Gouna</strong> and <strong data-start=\"1524\" data-end=\"1541\">Sahl Hasheesh</strong> or <strong>Sharm el Sheik</strong> offer&nbsp;<strong data-start=\"1548\" data-end=\"1566\">golden beaches</strong>, <strong data-start=\"1568\" data-end=\"1584\">calm lagoons</strong>, and <strong data-start=\"1590\" data-end=\"1618\">breathtaking coral reefs</strong> home to hundreds of colorful species &mdash; ideal for <strong data-start=\"1668\" data-end=\"1682\">snorkeling</strong>, <strong data-start=\"1684\" data-end=\"1694\">diving</strong>, <strong data-start=\"1696\" data-end=\"1720\">semi-submarine tours</strong>, and family-friendly sea adventures.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1759\" data-end=\"2003\">For thrill-seekers, the <strong data-start=\"1783\" data-end=\"1802\">Egyptian desert</strong> invites you into a land of wide-open spaces: <strong data-start=\"1848\" data-end=\"1863\">ATV safaris</strong>, <strong data-start=\"1865\" data-end=\"1884\">jeep adventures</strong>, <strong data-start=\"1886\" data-end=\"1901\">buggy rides</strong>, <strong data-start=\"1903\" data-end=\"1938\">bedouin dinners under the stars</strong>, and cultural immersion into traditions that survived millennia.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"2005\" data-end=\"2207\">Whether you want <strong data-start=\"2022\" data-end=\"2036\">relaxation</strong>, <strong data-start=\"2038\" data-end=\"2049\">romance</strong>, <strong data-start=\"2051\" data-end=\"2065\">family fun</strong>, or <strong data-start=\"2070\" data-end=\"2085\">exploration</strong>, Egypt delivers an unforgettable multi-sensory experience - a destination that stays with you long after you return home.</p>','uploads/custom-images/destination-2025-11-20-06-57-10-7241.png','uploads/custom-images/destination-2025-11-20-12-21-00-6383.png','EGYPT',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,0,0,'Egypt Travel Guide - Red Sea Adventures, Pyramids, Culture & Top Experiences',NULL,'<p>Discover Egypt: ancient wonders, Red Sea beaches, snorkeling, diving, desert safaris, boat trips, Paradise Island, Cairo tours, Luxor temples and the world&rsquo;s most iconic cultural landmarks. The ultimate destination for families, couples and adventure travelers.</p>','2025-11-20 10:21:00','2025-11-20 16:57:10',2,'Egypt, Egipt,  Hurghada, Sharm, Sharm El Sheik, Cairo, Luxor, Makadi, Sal Hashes, NIle, Egyptian Culture, Beach, Desert, Adventure, Snorkeling & Diving, Family, Pyramids, Luxor, Museums, Red Sea Beaches, Snorkeling, Diving, Coral Reefs'),(19,'PRAGUE','prague','<p><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-7abf1224-7fff-3991-5717-21c74670ac46\">PRAGUE - A fairytale city of spires, bridges, and timeless streets - where history, romance, and vibrant culture meet at every corner.</strong></p>','uploads/custom-images/destin