 Chania','<p>An expedition to one of the most stunning places in Crete, which could be named \"A visit to paradise\"... The route of the tour runs along the northern coast to Kissamos (Kastelli) Port, where the cruise begins around the gorgeous bay. After an hour arrival in Imeri Gramvousa.</p>\r\n<p>This uninhabited islet with intact nature is a natural reserve for many species of birds. A swim in the bay and visit to the ruins located on a 137 metre hill of the Venetian fortress from the 16th century, providing wonderful views of Balos Bay. Just a 15-minute boat ride divides the island from the picturesque Balos lagoon, where crystal clear water and wonderful relaxation awaits.An expedition to one of the most stunning places in Crete, which could be named \"A visit to paradise\"... The route of the tour runs along the northern coast to Kissamos (Kastelli) Port, where the cruise begins around the gorgeous bay. After an hour arrival in Imeri Gramvousa. This uninhabited islet with intact nature is a natural reserve for many species of birds. A swim in the bay and visit to the ruins located on a 137 metre hill of the Venetian fortress from the 16th century, providing wonderful views of Balos Bay. Just a 15-minute boat ride divides the island from the picturesque Balos lagoon, where crystal clear water and wonderful relaxation awaits.</p>','<p>An expedition to one of the most stunning places in Crete, which could be named \"A visit to paradise\"... The route of the tour runs along the northern coast to Kissamos (Kastelli) Port, where the cruise begins round the gorgeous bay.&nbsp;</p>','Gramvousa from Chania','<p>An expedition to one of the most stunning places in Crete, which could be named \"A visit to paradise\"... The route of the tour runs along the northern coast to Kissamos (Kastelli) P</p>','boat trip, family, seaview','\"[\\\"Transfer\\\",\\\"Boat trip\\\",\\\"Guide service\\\"]\"','\"[\\\"Tourist tax - approx. 1 EUR\\\"]\"','[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-05 09:02:38','2025-09-05 09:02:38'),(21,21,'en','Legendary Istanbul','<p>From the majestic wonders of the Byzantine and Ottoman empires to the vibrant atmosphere of local markets and teahouses, this experience is a perfect blend of iconic landmarks, authentic flavors, and local stories.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">8-9h guided tour of Sultanahmet: Hagia Sophia, Blue Mosque, Hippodrome, Topkapi Palace, Grand Bazaar, and free time for a traditional lunch.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Type of service:</strong> One-Day Tours - full day tour (8-9 h)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Type of Experience:</strong> Boat Trip, Culture &amp; History, Culinary Experience, Walking Tour</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Audience Fit:</strong> Family-Friendly, Couples, Groups, Solo Travelers, Senior-Friendly</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Discover</strong> Istanbul&rsquo;s legendary charm in a single day, guided by a local expert. Begin with Byzantine and Ottoman masterpieces - Hagia Sophia and the Blue Mosque - uncover their fascinating stories, and pause at the ancient Hippodrome. Continue with a local dining experience, tasting authentic Turkish dishes while hearing the host&rsquo;s stories. In the afternoon, explore Topkapi Palace, once home to the Ottoman sultans, before wandering the labyrinthine alleys of the Grand Bazaar. End the day with a cup of Turkish tea or coffee in a traditional teahouse and try shisha like the locals do.</p>\r\n<p><strong> This full-day tour offers a complete immersion into Istanbul&rsquo;s vibrant contrasts, blending iconic monuments with authentic experiences, street food, and local rituals<br><br></strong></p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1033\" data-end=\"1072\">Highlights (What you&rsquo;ll love!)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-start=\"1075\" data-end=\"1130\">Standing in awe before Hagia Sophia &amp; the Blue Mosque</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1075\" data-end=\"1130\">Walking the ancient Hippodrome, once the heart of Byzantine Constantinople</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1212\" data-end=\"1266\">Experiencing authentic Turkish flavours during lunch</li>\r\n<li>Exploring the opulent Topkapi Palace, the heart of the Ottoman Empire</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1269\" data-end=\"1349\">Exploring the labyrinth of the Grand Bazaar, one of the world&rsquo;s oldest markets</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1352\" data-end=\"1432\">Ending the day like a local - tea, coffee, and shisha in a traditional setting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-fa69b862-7fff-c5c7-7eca-237961e7ec2b\">&nbsp;</strong><br><br></p>','<p>A full-day (8-9h) guided tour through the heart of Istanbul&rsquo;s old city (Sultanahmet:), exploring its most iconic monuments (Hagia Sophia, Blue Mosque, Hippodrome, Topkapi Palace), traditional bazaars (Grand Bazaar), and authentic local flavours</p>','Classic Istanbul Day Tour – Hagia Sophia, Blue Mosque & Grand Bazaar','<p><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-b5ae0c73-7fff-0e24-7199-eebdece9072b\">Experience the best of Istanbul in one day. Our guided tour covers iconic sites like Hagia Sophia, Topkapi Palace, and the Grand Bazaar for an unforgettable cultural journey.</strong></p>','Istanbul, Istanbul tour, Istanbul day trip, city break Istanbul, Hagia Sophia, Blue Mosque, Topkapi Palace, Grand Bazaar, Istanbul guided tour, cultural tour Istanbul, Memento Trips Istanbul.','\"[\\\"8\\\\u20139h guided tour with a professional local guide\\\",\\\"Visits to: Hagia Sophia, Blue Mosque, Hippodrome, Topkapi Palace,