ainland, enjoy a walking tour of the charming and romantic Agios Nikolaos. The town today is an international cosmopolitan resort, located on three hills with an charming character and small winding streets. The next stop of the tour is Lake Vulismeni - the city\'s most precious treasure, with thousands of legends that make it even more attractive. The last point of the tour is a visit to the Vassilakis olive oil factory. This is a unique opportunity to see a demonstration of oil production. Time to by local specialties, then transfer to hotels.</p>','<p>What You\'ll See</p>\r\n<ul class=\"excursion-info__value\">\r\n<li>Swimming in the bay</li>\r\n<li>Charming Spinalonga</li>\r\n<li>Walk through the city of Agios Nikolaos</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>','spinalonga-and-agios-nikolaos','Spinalonga',NULL,NULL,10,12,49.00,49.00,NULL,25.00,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'\"[\\\"Transfer\\\",\\\"Guide service\\\",\\\"Boat trip\\\",\\\"Lunch\\\"]\"','\"[\\\"Entrance fee to the Spinalonga fortress - approx. 20 EUR per person\\\"]\"','4','10','[\"English\"]',NULL,'[\"5\"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,1,1,0,NULL,'strada Grigore Moisil, nr. 6','atena@behappydigital.com','0745602932',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-03 10:59:45','2025-09-18 09:42:52',1,4,1,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(20,'Gramvousa from Chania','<p>An expedition to one of the most stunning places in Crete, which could be named \"A visit to paradise\"... The route of the tour runs along the northern coast to Kissamos (Kastelli) Port, where the cruise begins around the gorgeous bay. After an hour arrival in Imeri Gramvousa.</p>\r\n<p>This uninhabited islet with intact nature is a natural reserve for many species of birds. A swim in the bay and visit to the ruins located on a 137 metre hill of the Venetian fortress from the 16th century, providing wonderful views of Balos Bay. Just a 15-minute boat ride divides the island from the picturesque Balos lagoon, where crystal clear water and wonderful relaxation awaits.An expedition to one of the most stunning places in Crete, which could be named \"A visit to paradise\"... The route of the tour runs along the northern coast to Kissamos (Kastelli) Port, where the cruise begins around the gorgeous bay. After an hour arrival in Imeri Gramvousa. This uninhabited islet with intact nature is a natural reserve for many species of birds. A swim in the bay and visit to the ruins located on a 137 metre hill of the Venetian fortress from the 16th century, providing wonderful views of Balos Bay. Just a 15-minute boat ride divides the island from the picturesque Balos lagoon, where crystal clear water and wonderful relaxation awaits.</p>','<p>An expedition to one of the most stunning places in Crete, which could be named \"A visit to paradise\"... The route of the tour runs along the northern coast to Kissamos (Kastelli) Port, where the cruise begins round the gorgeous bay.&nbsp;</p>','gramvousa-from-chania','Chania',NULL,NULL,10,12,79.00,79.00,75.00,50.00,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'\"[\\\"Transfer\\\",\\\"Boat trip\\\",\\\"Guide service\\\"]\"','\"[\\\"Tourist tax - approx. 1 EUR\\\"]\"','all day','no limit','[]','Mobile Voucher',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,1,1,0,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xHhVf05j2qo','Strada Toma Socolescu 23C','atena@super40','0745602932',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-05 09:02:38','2025-09-18 09:42:15',1,2,1,0,NULL,'\"A visit to paradise\"..','Langa hotel Ramada','https://maps.app.goo.gl/yZaK14HGYb5dhwmY6',1),(21,'Legendary Istanbul','<p>From the majestic wonders of the Byzantine and Ottoman empires to the vibrant atmosphere of local markets and teahouses, this experience is a perfect blend of iconic landmarks, authentic flavors, and local stories.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">8-9h guided tour of Sultanahmet: Hagia Sophia, Blue Mosque, Hippodrome, Topkapi Palace, Grand Bazaar, and free time for a traditional lunch.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Type of service:</strong> One-Day Tours - full day tour (8-9 h)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Type of Experience:</strong> Boat Trip, Culture &amp; History, Culinary Experience, Walking Tour</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Audience Fit:</strong> Family-Friendly, Couples, Groups, Solo Travelers, Senior-Friendly</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Discover</strong> Istanbul&rsquo;s legendary charm in a single day, guided by a local expert. Begin with Byzantine and Ottoman masterpieces - Hagia Sophia and the Blue Mosque - uncover their fascinating stories, and pause at the ancient Hippodrome. Continue with a local dining experience, tasting authentic Turkish dishes while hearing the host&rsquo;s stories. In the afternoon, explore Topkapi Palace, once home to the Ottoman sultans, before wandering the labyrinthine alleys of the Grand Bazaar. End the day with a cup of Turkish tea or coffee in a traditional teahouse and try shisha like the locals do.</p>\r\n<p><strong> This full-day tour offers a complete immersion into Istanbul&rsquo;s vibrant contrasts, blending iconic monuments with authentic experiences, street food, and local rituals<br><br></strong></p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1033\" data-end=\"1072\">Highlights (What you&rsquo;ll love!)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-start=\"1075\" data-end=\"1130\">Standing in awe before Hagia Sophia &amp; the Blue Mosque</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1075\" data-end=\"1130\">Walking the ancient Hippodrome, once the heart of Byzantine Constantinople</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1212\" data-end=\"1266\">Experiencing authentic Turkish flavours during lunch</li>\r\n<li>Exploring the opulent Topkapi Palace, the heart of the Ottoman Empire</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1269\" data-end=\"1349\">Exploring the labyrinth of the Grand Bazaar, one of the world&rsquo;s oldest markets</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1352\" data-end=\"1432\">Ending the day like a local - tea, coffee, and shisha in a traditional setting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-fa69b862-7fff-c5c7-7eca-237961e7ec2b\">&nbsp;</strong><br><br></p>','<p>A full-day (8-9h) guided tour through the heart of Istanbul&rsquo;s old city (Sultanahmet:), exploring its most iconic monuments (Hagia Sophia, Blue Mosque, Hippodrome, Topkapi Palace), traditional bazaars (Grand Bazaar), and authentic local flavours</p>','legendary-istanbul','Turkey - Istanbul',NULL,NULL,2,14,69.00,80.00,15.00,33.00,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'\"[\\\"8\\\\u20139h guided tour with a professional local guide\\\",\\\"Visits to: Hagia Sophia, Blue Mosque, Hippodrome, Topkapi Palace, Grand Bazaar\\\",\\\"Lunch in a traditional Turkish restaurant (fixed menu)\\\",\\\"Turkish tea or coffee in a local teahouse\\\",\\\"Shisha tasting (optional - extra charge!)\\\",\\\"All entrance fees to the mentioned attractions\\\"]\"','\"[\\\"Hotel pick-up\\\\\\/drop-off: Hotel Transfer = Transportation to\\\\\\/from meeting point (unless booked separately!)\\\",\\\"Personal expenses (souvenirs, extra food & drinks)\\\",\\\"Tips for guide\\\\\\/driver\\\",\\\"Travel insurance\\\",\\\"Drinks other than those mentioned in the program\\\",\\\"Optional activities (e.g., shisha, extra purchases at the Grand Bazaar)\\\"]\"','8-9 h','No restrictions','[]','Mobile voucher or printed tiket',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,1,1,0,NULL,'ISTANBUL strada mare','email@partener.tr','070',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-12 14:12:56','2025-09-29 12:28:11',1,1,4,2,'{\"infant\":{\"enabled\":false,\"count\":0,\"price\":null,\"min_age\":null,\"max_age\":null},\"baby\":{\"enabled\":true,\"count\":10,\"price\":100,\"min_age\":2,\"max_age\":4},\"child\":{\"enabled\":true,\"count\":10,\"price\":120,\"min_age\":5,\"max_age\":17},\"adult\":{\"enabled\":true,\"count\":10,\"price\":140,\"min_age\":18,\"max_age\":120}}','From Hagia Sophia to the Grand Bazaar - a legendary journey through Istanbul in one day.',NULL,NULL,1),(22,'Classic Munich - History & Traditions','<p>&nbsp;Discover Munich&rsquo;s historic heart in a guided walking tour starting at Marienplatz, with the famous Glockenspiel and Frauenkirche. Explore Viktualienmarkt, a lively food market filled with local flavours. Midday, enjoy a Bavarian meal in a traditional beer hall with local brews, sausages, and pretzels. In the afternoon, continue with the English Garden and its river surfers, before ending the day in a relaxed biergarten under the chestnut trees.<br><br></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">8-9h guided tour of Munich: Marienplatz, with the famous Glockenspiel and Frauenkirche, Viktualienmarkt, lunch included, English Garden and optional dinner in a biergarten.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Type of service:</strong> One-Day Tours - full day tour (8-9 h)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Type of Experience:</strong> Culture &amp; History, Culinary Experience, Walking Tour</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Audience Fit:</strong> Family-Friendly, Couples, Groups, Solo Travelers, Senior-Friendly</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span class=\"citation-36 citation-end-36\">&nbsp;</span></spa