INSERT INTO `testimonial_trasnlations` VALUES (1,1,'en','Anna M.','TURKYE, ANTALYA, Alanya Boat Trip - Pirate Cruise & Mediterranean Adventure','Booking our Antalya excursions through Memento Trips was the easiest decision of our holiday. Everything was clear, prices were fair, and the experience was beyond expectations.','2025-01-15 08:30:46','2025-11-26 14:46:43'),(2,2,'en','Sonia McKinney','Greece, Crete, Lassithi Plateau & CretAquarium','Everything was as described, the guide was a nice person. We had a lot of fun.','2025-01-15 08:32:53','2025-11-26 14:38:22'),(3,3,'en','Cynthia Leeland','Greece, Crete, Elafonissi: Pink Sand Beach & Exotic Landscapes','Elafonisi is so beautiful. Maybe not as pink as in the pictures or the description, but very special, unique and fun for a few hours of fun and sunbathing.','2025-01-15 08:37:56','2025-11-26 14:43:31'),(7,1,'pl','Marvin McKinney','15th Batch Students','The pandemic has accelerated the shift to online and hybrid learning models. Platforms like Coursera, edX, and university-specific online programs offer flexibility and accessibility to a wider audience.','2025-08-15 14:36:30','2025-08-15 14:36:30'),(8,2,'pl','Sarvin McKinney','10th Batch Students','Platforms like Coursera, edX, and university-specific online programs offer flexibility and\r\n                  accessibility to a wider audience. The pandemic has accelerated the shift to online and hybrid\r\n                  learning models.','2025-08-15 14:36:30','2025-08-15 14:36:30'),(9,3,'pl','Karvin McSinney','8th Batch Students','Frameworks such as Coursera, edX, and university-specific online programs provide greater flexibility and accessibility to a broader audience. The pandemic significantly accelerated learning models.','2025-08-15 14:36:30','2025-08-15 14:36:30');
