ts. (e.g., Heraklion, Agia Pelagia, Hersonissos, Malia)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>&euro;74</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&euro;37.50</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>West-Central Coast:</strong>&nbsp;Areas just west of the &euro;65 zone. (e.g., Fodele, Bali)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>&euro;85</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&euro;42.50</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Far Eastern Coast:</strong>&nbsp;Remote Eastern destinations. (e.g., Agios Nikolaos, Elounda)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Not Available</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>N/A</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Far West:</strong>&nbsp;Areas around&nbsp;<strong>Rethymno</strong>, Georgioupolis, and Kavros.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<strong>&nbsp;Location:</strong> Central Eastern Crete',NULL,'8-9 h',NULL,NULL,1,'2025-10-16 12:32:37','2025-10-16 12:32:37'),(46,30,'Lassithi Plateau & CretAquarium Itinerary',1,'<p><strong data-start=\"4606\" data-end=\"4629\">Map Style Itinerary</strong><br data-start=\"4629\" data-end=\"4632\">🟢 <strong data-start=\"4635\" data-end=\"4645\">Start:</strong> Pick-up from hotels (Heraklion &ndash; Hersonissos &ndash; Malia area)<br data-start=\"4704\" data-end=\"4707\">➡️ <strong data-start=\"4710\" data-end=\"4726\">CretAquarium</strong> &ndash; marine life and Mediterranean wonders<br data-start=\"4766\" data-end=\"4769\">➡️ <strong data-start=\"4772\" data-end=\"4802\">Kera Kardiotissa Monastery</strong> &ndash; sacred icon &amp; pilgrimage site<br data-start=\"4834\" data-end=\"4837\">➡️ <strong data-start=\"4840\" data-end=\"4859\">Psychro Village</strong> &ndash; traditional pottery demonstration<br data-start=\"4895\" data-end=\"4898\">🍴 <strong data-start=\"4901\" data-end=\"4915\">Lunch stop</strong> &ndash; free time or optional local taverna<br data-start=\"4953\" data-end=\"4956\">➡️ <strong data-start=\"4959\" data-end=\"4981\">Lasinthos Eco Park</strong> &ndash; traditional Cretan life &amp; local animals<br data-start=\"5023\" data-end=\"5026\">➡️ <strong data-start=\"5029\" data-end=\"5054\">Cretan Knife Workshop</strong> &ndash; discover the legend and craftsmanship<br data-start=\"5094\" data-end=\"5097\">🔵 <strong data-start=\"5100\" data-end=\"5111\">Return:</strong> Transfer back to hotel pick-up points<br><br><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>STANDARD RATES/PRICES:<br>infants under 2 years old - FREE!&nbsp;</strong><br>- For hotels located in: Agia Pelagia; Lygaria; Ammoudara; Heraklion; Hersonissos; Kokkini Hani; Gournes; Gouves; Analipsi; Anissaras; Stalida; Malia; -&nbsp;<strong>Adults: 65 &euro; / Children 2-12 years: 32.5 &euro; (50% of Adult price)</strong><br>- For hotels located in: Agios Nikolaos; Ammoudara (Ag.Nikolaos); Elounda; Istron; Sissi; Vathi; -&nbsp;<strong>extra charge 20 euro/adult&nbsp;</strong>=&nbsp;<strong>Adults: 85 &euro; / Children 2-12 years: 42.5 &euro; (50% of Adult price)</strong><br>- For hotels located in: Fodele; Bali; -&nbsp;<strong>extra charge 9 euro/adult = </strong><strong>Adults: 74 &euro; / Children 2-12 years: 37 &euro;</strong>&nbsp;<strong>(50% of Adult price)</strong><br>The excursion is&nbsp;<strong>NOT valid for hotels located in</strong>: Adelianos Kambos; Panormo; Pigianos Kampos (Rethymno); Platanias Rethymno; Rethymno; Sfakaki; Georgioupolis; Kavros.</p>\r\n\r\n<strong>&nbsp;</strong>','Central Eastern Crete','8-9 h',NULL,NULL,2,'2025-10-16 12:39:15','2025-10-16 12:39:15'),(47,31,'Gramvousa & Balos Lagoon – Pink Sands & Turquoise Waters',1,'<p>🟢 <strong data-start=\"4477\" data-end=\"4487\">Start:</strong> Pick-up from hotels (Heraklion &ndash; Hersonissos &ndash; Rethymno &ndash; Bali area)<br data-start=\"4556\" data-end=\"4559\">➡️ <strong data-start=\"4562\" data-end=\"4591\">Transfer to Kissamos Port</strong> &ndash; embarkation for the boat cruise<br data-start=\"4625\" data-end=\"4628\">🛥️ <strong data-start=\"4632\" data-end=\"4660\">Sail to Gramvousa Island</strong> &ndash; visit the Venetian fortress &amp; enjoy panoramic views<br data-start=\"4714\" data-end=\"4717\">➡️ <strong data-start=\"4720\" data-end=\"4748\">Continue to Balos Lagoon</strong> &ndash; swim, sunbathe, and relax in paradise<br data-start=\"4788\" data-end=\"4791\">🍴 <strong data-start=\"4794\" data-end=\"4812\">Optional lunch</strong> &ndash; onboard or at local taverna near the port<br data-start=\"4856\" data-end=\"4859\">🔵 <strong data-start=\"4862\" data-end=\"4873\">Return:</strong> Afternoon transfer back to hotel pick-up points</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2025-10-20 13:53:22','2025-10-20 13:53:22'),(48,31,'The Hotel Pick Up services, areas and prices',1,'<p data-start=\"262\" data-end=\"474\">The <strong data-start=\"266\" data-end=\"294\">pick-up service in Crete</strong> for the Balos &amp; Gramvousa excursion is divided into <strong data-start=\"347\" data-end=\"373\">three main price tiers</strong>, based on the <strong data-start=\"388\" data-end=\"425\">distance from the Rethymno Region</strong>, where the departure port (Kissamos) is located:</p>\r\n<ol data-start=\"476\" data-end=\"1037\">\r\n<li data-start=\"476\" data-end=\"636\">\r\n<p data-start=\"479\" data-end=\"636\"><strong data-start=\"479\" data-end=\"551\">Zone 1 &ndash; Rethymno Region &amp; Nearby Areas (Closest to Departure Port):</strong><br data-start=\"551\" data-end=\"554\">The most affordable option, as the distance to Kissamos Port is the shortest.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"638\" data-end=\"835\">\r\n<p data-start=\"641\" data-end=\"835\"><strong data-start=\"641\" data-end=\"688\">Zone 2 &ndash; Central Crete (Moderate Distance):</strong><br data-start=\"688\" data-end=\"691\">Includes areas like Bali and Fodele, located midway between Heraklion and Rethymno. Prices are slightly higher due to longer transfer time.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"837\" data-end=\"1037\">\r\n<p data-start=\"840\" data-end=\"1037\"><strong data-start=\"840\" data-end=\"898\">Zone 3 &ndash; Eastern Crete (Furthest from Departure Port):</strong><br data-start=\"898\" data-end=\"901\">Covers the main resorts around Heraklion and Hersonissos. Prices are the highest, reflecting the longest travel distance to the port.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p data-start=\"1039\" data-end=\"1153\">👉 The <strong data-start=\"1046\" data-end=\"1062\">further east</strong> your hotel is located, the <strong data-start=\"1090\" data-end=\"1100\">higher</strong> the transfer cost and therefore the excursion price.<br><br></p>\r\n<table class=\"w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)\" data-start=\"1197\" data-end=\"2072\">\r\n\r\n<tr data-start=\"1197\" data-end=\"1299\">\r\n<th data-start=\"1197\" data-end=\"1216\" data-col-size=\"lg\"><strong data-start=\"1199\" data-end=\"1215\">Pick-Up Area</strong></th>\r\n<th data-start=\"1216\" data-end=\"1234\" data-col-size=\"sm\"><strong data-start=\"1218\" data-end=\"1233\">Adult Price</strong></th>\r\n<th data-start=\"1234\" data-end=\"1263\" data-col-size=\"sm\"><strong data-start=\"1236\" data-end=\"1262\">Child Price (2&ndash;12 yrs)</strong></th>\r\n<th data-start=\"1263\" data-end=\"1286\" data-col-size=\"sm\"><strong data-start=\"1265\" data-end=\"1285\">Infant (0&ndash;2 yrs)</strong></th>\r\n<th data-start=\"1286\" data-end=\"1299\" data-col-size=\"md\"><strong data-start=\"1288\" data-end=\"1297\">Notes</strong></th>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n<tr data-start=\"1404\" data-end=\"1598\">\r\n<td data-start=\"1404\" data-end=\"1506\" data-col-size=\"lg\"><strong data-start=\"1406\" data-end=\"1505\">Adelianos Kambos, Panormo, Pigianos Kampos (Rethymno), Rethymno, Sfakaki, Georgioupolis, Kavros</strong></td>\r\n<td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-start=\"1506\" data-end=\"1517\"><strong data-start=\"1508\" data-end=\"1516\">68 &euro;</strong></td>\r\n<td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-start=\"1517\" data-end=\"1540\"><strong data-start=\"1519\" data-end=\"1527\">34 &euro;</strong> (50% adult)</td>\r\n<td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-start=\"1540\" data-end=\"1551\"><strong data-start=\"1542\" data-end=\"1550\">FREE</strong></td>\r\n<td data-col-size=\"md\" data-start=\"1551\" data-end=\"1598\">Closest to departure port (Rethymno Region)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr data-start=\"1599\" data-end=\"1713\">\r\n<td data-start=\"1599\" data-end=\"1618\" data-col-size=\"lg\"><strong data-start=\"1601\" data-end=\"1617\">Fodele, Bali</strong></td>\r\n<td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-start=\"1618\" data-end=\"1629\"><strong data-start=\"1620\" data-end=\"1628\">74 &euro;</strong></td>\r\n<td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-start=\"1629\" data-end=\"1652\"><strong data-start=\"1631\" data-end=\"1639\">37 &euro;</strong> (50% adult)</td>\r\n<td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-start=\"1652\" data-end=\"1663\"><strong data-start=\"1654\" data-end=\"1662\">FREE</strong></td>\r\n<td data-col-size=\"md\" data-start=\"1663\" data-end=\"1713\">Mid-distance zone between Heraklion &amp; Rethymno</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr data-start=\"1714\" data-end=\"1932\">\r\n<td data-start=\"1714\" data-end=\"1845\" data-col-size=\"lg\"><strong data-start=\"1716\" data-end=\"1844\">Agia Pelagia, Lygaria, Ammoudara, Heraklion, Hersonissos, Kokkini Hani, Gournes, Gouves, Analipsi, Anissaras, Stalida, Malia</strong></td>\r\n<td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-start=\"1845\" data-end=\"1856\"><strong data-start=\"1847\" data-end=\"1855\">84 &euro;</strong></td>\r\n<td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-start=\"1856\" data-end=\"1879\"><strong data-start=\"1858\" data-end=\"1866\">42 &euro;</strong> (50% adult)</td>\r\n<td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-start=\"1879\" data-end=\"1890\"><strong data-start=\"1881\" data-end=\"1889\">FREE</strong></td>\r\n<td data-col-size=\"md\" data-start=\"1890\" data-end=\"1932\">Farthest transfer zone (Eastern Crete)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr data-start=\"1933\" data-end=\"2072\">\r\n<td data-start=\"1933\" data-end=\"2011\" data-col-size=\"lg\"><strong data-start=\"1935\" data-end=\"2010\">Agios Nikolaos, Ammoudara (Ag. Nikolaos), Elounda, Istron, Sissi, Vathi</strong></td>\r\n<td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-start=\"2011\" data-end=\"2